tosdr.case: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision

title: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision
quoteText:
Failure to Enforce

The failure of either party to enforce at any time, or for any period of time, the provisions hereof shall not be construed to be a waiver of such provisions or of the right of such party to enforce each and every such provision.
